flowchart TD
    A[Dispatch exposure active] --> B{Bridge consumed / exposure closed?}
    B -- No --> C[Remain passive_exposed]
    B -- Yes --> D[Exposure release]
    D --> E[Dispatch completed]
    E --> F[Container reset_pending]
    F --> G{Safe point available?}
    G -- No --> H[Wait / report pending]
    G -- Yes --> I[Moderator claims reset]
    I --> J[Apply default empty container profile]
    J --> K[Clear slot states to empty]
    K --> L[Clear container time range]
    L --> M[Invalidate old references]
    M --> N[Container default_empty]
    N --> O[Container ingress_ready]
    O --> P[RoundManager may admit to ingress waiting list]
